1. For developer:
    - step 1: install python 3x.
    - step 2: restored database.
    - step 3: open project.
    - step 4: install library using: pip install -r requirements.txt
    - step 5: config settings.py file

2. For deployment:
    - pythonanywhere.com: https://help.pythonanywhere.com/pages/DeployExistingDjangoProject/
    - windows server : http://blog.mattwoodward.com/2016/07/running-django-application-on-windows.html

